# Full Context Test
@diagram|id:context-test|type:flow|purpose:Test all context sections|direction:TD

@use-when|condition:testing context sections
@use-when|condition:need comprehensive output|threshold:all sections
@use-not|condition:minimal diagrams|reason:too much overhead

@node|id:A|label:Start
@node|id:B|label:End
@edge|from:A|to:B

@component|name:Main Script|file:scripts/main.py|does:Entry point
@component|name:Helper|file:scripts/helper.py|does:Utility functions

@config|param:timeout|value:30s|note:Configurable
@config|param:retries|value:3

